  <h1>50 Cent</h1>
  <p>From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</p>

  <p>
    Curtis James Jackson III, known professionally as 50 Cent, is an American
    rapper, actor, and businessman<sup><a href="#ref1">[1]</a></sup>. He was
    born on July 6, 1975, in Queens, New York City<sup><a href="#ref2">[2]</a></sup>.
    He is known for his rough upbringing and his rise to become one of the
    best selling rappers in the world<sup><a href="#ref3">[3]</a></sup>.
  </p>

